   <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1666_dai_lns235ms_v_r.jpg"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>هو المعز</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>شجاعت اطوار
               <persName ref="#sultanMuhammad">سلطانمحمد</persName>
                بتوجه خاطر مستظهر بوده بداند درینولا از روی تقریر
               <persName ref="#wazirKhan">وزیری خانی</persName>
               <lb/>
               <persName ref="#ahmadBegKhan">احمد بیگ خان</persName>
                و از مضمون عرضه
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتم</persName>
                چودری
               <placeName ref="#dhar">دهار</placeName>
                معلوم گردید که چودری مذکور و چودری
               <lb/>
               <placeName ref="#nalcha">نعلجه</placeName>
                زر
               <add>بابت</add>
                ضامنی
               <add>چودری</add>
               <placeName ref="#amjhera">امجهره</placeName>
                سوای زری که دعوی آن بمقتضای ضامنی بچودری
               <placeName ref="#kampel">کنپیل</placeName>
                دارند بوصول
               <lb/>رسانیدند و از آنجمله قلیلی باقی مانده لهذا نوشته می شود که آنچه از بابت حصه
               چودری
               <lb/>
               <placeName ref="#dhar">دهار</placeName>
                که
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتم</persName>
                باشد نزد او باقی باشد تا دام آخر پی اینمال بوصول رسانیده خود را
               <lb/>بحضور برساند و بواسطه اخذ زری که دعوی آن بچودری
               <placeName ref="#kampel">کنپیل</placeName>
                دارند بالفعل مزاحم نشود
               <lb/>که ما در حضور خود چودری
               <placeName ref="#kampel">کنپیل</placeName>
                را طلبداشته بمقتضای عدالت این معامله را فیصل خواهیم داد
               <lb/>حسب المسطور بعمل آورد و باقی وجه حصه چودری
               <placeName ref="#dhar">دهار</placeName>
                و
               <placeName ref="#nalcha">نعلجه</placeName>
                را تا دام تحصیل نموده بیاورد
               <lb/>
                درینباب تاکید داند فی التاریخ
               <date calendar="#julus">
                  <num>۲۷</num>
                   محرم الحرم سنه
                  <num>۹</num>
               </date>
                قلمی شد
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g><note>This last line is written on the left margin, which is unusual. Scribes
                  typically wrapped text to the right margin if they ran out of space.</note>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p>
               <app>
                  <rdg cert="high">بموجب مسطور عمل شد</rdg>
                  <rdg cert="low">بر حسب حضور تحریر شد</rdg>
               </app>
               <g ref="#baiz">بیض</g>
               <lb rend="empty"/><stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
                     <persName ref="#wazirKhan">وزیر خان</persName>
                     <unclear>مرید</unclear>
                      بادشاه
                     <persName ref="#aurangzebAlamgir">عالمگیر</persName>
                  </mentioned></stamp></p>
         </div>
         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1666_dai_lns235ms_v_v.jpg"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="per" type="laterAddition" rend="top centre">
            <p>
               <foreign>نمبر</foreign>
               <num>۲۱</num>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div1" xml:id="trans_div1">
            <p>He [God] is respected</p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div2" xml:id="trans_div2">
            <p>
               <lb/>Courageous in Manner
               <persName ref="#sultanMuhammad">Sultan Muhammad</persName>, being comforted by the favour of remembrance<note>I.e. being noticed by the Lord</note>, 
               know that recently from the declaration of the servant of
               <persName ref="#wazirKhan">Wazir Khan</persName>,
               <lb/>
               <persName ref="#ahmadBegKhan">Ahmad Beg Khan</persName>, and from the contents of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_arz">ʿarz</ref> of
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam [Das]</persName>
               <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> of
               <placeName ref="#dhar">Dhar</placeName>, it became known that the said <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> and the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref>
               <lb/>of
               <placeName ref="#nalcha">Nalcha</placeName>
               delivered the money for the security of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> of
               <placeName ref="#amjhera">Amjhera</placeName>,
                except for the money that they have claimed for the surety of the
               <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> of
               <placeName ref="#kampel">Kanpil [Kampel]</placeName>.
               <lb/>And from that total amount, a little [money] is due, and hence it is written that
               that which is the share of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref>
               <lb/>of
               <placeName ref="#dhar">Dhar</placeName> – that is,
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam</persName> – is outstanding from him. Until the last <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_dam">dam</ref> for this amount has been
               deposited, he should
               <lb/>bring himself to the Lord. And for procuring the money that they have claimed
               from the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> of
               <placeName ref="#kampel">Kanpil [Kampel]</placeName>, let there be no obstruction
               <lb/> so that we will summon the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> of
               <placeName ref="#kampel">Kanpil [Kampel]</placeName>
                to our presence and decide this matter in accordance with the law.
               <lb/>Execute [it] as written. And let the remaining sum for the share of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> of
               <placeName ref="#dhar">Dhar</placeName>
               and
               <placeName ref="#nalcha">Nalcha</placeName>
               until the [last] <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_dam">dam</ref> be brought and deposited.
               <lb/>Know this matter as settled. Written on the date of 
               <date calendar="#julus">27 Muharram the Holy, [regnal] year 9</date>. </p>
            <closer>
               <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further.</g>
            </closer>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div3" xml:id="trans_div3">
            <p>
               <app>
                  <rdg cert="high">Executed as written.</rdg>
                  <rdg cert="low">Written according to the Lord.</rdg>
               </app>
               <g ref="#baiz">Ended.</g>
               <lb rend="empty"/><stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned>
                     <persName ref="#wazirKhan">Wazir Khan</persName>
                     <unclear>disciple</unclear>
                      of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_badshah">Badshah</ref>
                     <persName ref="#aurangzebAlamgir">Alamgir</persName>
                  </mentioned></stamp>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div4" xml:id="trans_div4">
            <p>Number 21</p>
         </div>
      </body>
